&lt;li&gt;Execute on operational, support, special research, or administrative projects for the Ops Team or within our portfolio companies, helping our CEOs be successful, to include supporting periodic CEO gatherings and best-practice-sharing events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
